<div class="conainall">
  <div class="bnr_bg">
    <div class="container">
      <h4>Thank you for your application.<br>
        Please confirm the details below.</h4>
    </div>
  </div>



  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div class="content_area">
      <div class="data_all">
        <h5>Please confirm your loan amount</h5>
        <a>You have applied for a loan between </a>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-primary w-75 mt-1">
            Between £5,000 - £15,000
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <div class="form-check form-switch cstm_mar">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="flexSwitchCheckChecked" checked data-parsley-required="true" data-parsley-group="block-2"
            data-parsley-required-message="Please accept our terms and conditions" required>
            <label class="form-check-label" for="flexSwitchCheckChecked">I confirm these details are
              true</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3">
          You have also been approved to apply for a homeowner loan of at least £15,000. We would like to
          pass you details to our partners at The Personal Finance Centre who may be able to assist you
          further. They won’t need much of your time, so look out for a call from an 01482 number shortly
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="form-check">
        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault">
        <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault">
          I consent to my details being passed to The Personal Finance Centre
        </label>
      </div>
      <p>
        I consent to The Personal Finance Centre contacting <br>
        me via the following channels
      </p>
      <div class="form-check form-check0">
        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault1">
        <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault1">
          SMS
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="form-check form-check0">
        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault2">
        <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault2">
          Email
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="form-check form-check0">
        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault3">
        <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault3">
          Phone
        </label>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center">
        By clicking continue I confirm that these details are true and accurate and<br>
        that I have read the terms and conditions and privacy policy
      </p>
      <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-12 mx-auto">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg col-md-4 nextStep" id="btn-continue"  type="button">Continue</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center">
        Secured Loan Representative Example: If you borrow £15,000 over 10 years at an annual interest rate
        of 7.40% you would make 120 payments of £202.03 per month. The total amount repayable will be
        £24243.55 (This includes a lender fee of £595 and a broker fee of £1500 which have been added to the
        loan). Total charge for credit will be £9243.55. Overall cost for comparison is 10.456% APRC
        representative. The Personal Finance Centre is a leading broker and not a lender.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

